data.title: Post Your mp3 Playlist! (Warning, long load times ahead)
data.meta_description: You can do this by opening up your Winamp (2.x, I think) and choosing to view your playlist. Next go down to those buttons on the bottom and click Misc. Options > Sort List > Select Sort List By Title. Then go to Misc Options again and click twice and select Generate HTML playlist from the options. Then copy and paste. Here's my more recent downloads: 197 tracks in playlist, average track length: 3:46 Playlist length: 12 hours 24 minutes 52 seconds Right-click here to save
